{"tid":1488121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想多謝今朝個靚姐，推到有人比佢知","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:57.000Z","uid":196227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebf9467f478a7101d0f7abfe7546f6f1f3840dd","tid":1488121,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"今朝8:45左右去咗西灣河嗰頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到閘機嗰層，聽到有人嘈<br />\n以為又係藍絲廢老發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽聽下聽到黑警之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後開始明佢單拖屌緊個白頭西裝廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中途有個路過靚仔大聲支持佢<br />\n<br />\n我連一句「罵得好」都唔敢講走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個女人都敢大大聲單拖屌柒廢老<br />\n我真係冇撚用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我認我無能冇去幫手同大聲支持佢<br />\n由朝早內疚到夜晚<br />\n想開post多謝佢<br />\n想比佢知路過既人都支持佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過知道既都留句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚型呀港女<br />\n<br />\n824<br />\n825<br />\n831"},{"pid":"1c0e7cd15dc74c99dcae7aa2656c3d02e0bc333b","tid":1488121,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"靚女多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你真係好撚型"},{"pid":"f4ddcd635b918f893f0b8b59ddb0d6436c62305a","tid":1488121,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"你既聲線下面嗰層都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd8bb882ffbb19a5c34fadebfda33957a65af99","tid":1488121,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHK